flowchart LR
    START([tick]) --> LOAD_AGENTS[Load .meta.json files]
    LOAD_AGENTS --> ENUM[Enumerate features]
    ENUM --> FOR_EACH{For each feature}
    FOR_EACH --> MTIME{README mtime\nchanged?}
    MTIME -->|yes| PARSE[Parse README]
    MTIME -->|no| USE_CACHE[Use cached tasks]
    PARSE --> COMPUTE[compute_feature]
    USE_CACHE --> COMPUTE
    COMPUTE --> FOR_EACH
    FOR_EACH -->|done| SERIALIZE[Serialize JSON]
    SERIALIZE --> HASH{String ==\nprevious?}
    HASH -->|yes| SKIP_WRITE([Skip write])
    HASH -->|no| WRITE_STATE[Write state.json]
    WRITE_STATE --> DONE([Sleep 1s])
    SKIP_WRITE --> DONE
